# Local data cruft — the REAL store lives in the sibling research-system-rag-data/ dir.
# A relative-path run can create empty/partial copies of these at the repo root (OG-33) — the
# empty papers.db is the exact file build_mcp_server used to fall back to (the fake Recall@10=0.000
# trap, fixed in T-DOC56). Never track them here.
papers.db
papers.db-shm
papers.db-wal
pdf_cache/
blobs/

# Agent worktrees / local Claude state — never track.
.claude/
.worktrees/
.gpu.lock

# Graphify knowledge-graph output — a local, regenerated artifact (4MB+ graph.json + HTML,
# rebuilt free by the post-commit hook / `graphify update .`). The `.graphifyignore` corpus
# filter IS tracked; the generated graph is not. Flip this line off to version the graph across
# worktrees (a union merge-driver is already registered in .gitattributes for that case).
graphify-out/
